data.description: Welcome home to Worland, Wyoming! Located on a beautiful tree lined street, and offering an assumable VA loan at 2.75% APR, this modest home has the potential to shine bright! The enclosed front porch welcomes you in. The formal dining room is at the heart of this home, and is surrounded by the living room, kitchen, and bedrooms. Each of the two bedrooms offer walk in closets, a rare find! This home exterior features of the property include ample parking including a detached garage, a fenced yard, and the lot is in close proximity to local shopping! Call a licensed real estate agent to see it in person!
